User Stats Dashboard — macro, cumulative view

			Total games played

			Win rate (%)

			Average score

			Current win streak (Longest)



			Win Rate Trends (line chart / last week)

			Wins/Losses/Draws (pie / over time)

			Playtime (per day / last week)



			Total Playtime

			Most frequent opponent

			Most Wins

			Most Losses


Game Sessions Dashboard — micro, per-match log

		Table of all matches (paginated), sorted newest-first

			Date/time of match

			Opponent name

			Result (win/loss/draw)

			Final score (user vs opponent)

			Game mode

			Match duration

		Filters

			Date range

			Opponent

			Result type

			Game mode

		Per-match drill-down (clickable row or modal):

			Same data as above, plus:

			Start and end timestamps

			Score progression (if tracked over rounds)

			Notes or highlights (if supported)

			Replay link (if supported)